# VERSION
v0.15.1

# Changelog
- v0.15.1
    - Added SWHY stock category
- v0.15.0
    - Added phase I of CacheEngine.
        - Added Arrow + mmap
        - Added compaction API
        - Added Partition Resolver
        - Added unit tests for cache engine
        - Added multiple data dimension in workbench
- v0.14.0
    - Added Task Cancel API, invoked by cronjob.
    - Added Timeout control for task engine.
    - Added exchange support for filtering stock list.
    - Fixed issue of using wrong parameters in STOCK_ZH_A_HIST.
- v0.13.1
    - Added exchange filter in STOCK_ZH_A_LIST
- v0.13.0
