- v0.12.1
    - Added skewness, kurtosis, support and breakout indicators.
- v0.12.0
    - Extracted `analyzers/` and `data_providers/` into independent module folders under `strategy_engine`, aligning with the existing `strategies/` structure.
    - Added Strategy Research Workbench.
- v0.11.1
    - Fixed design flaws of strategy engine.
    - Rename backtrade units to bt_engine.
